      "description": "Presented in commendable mechanical and aesthetic order, this vehicle exemplifies a commitment to consistent maintenance and reliable performance. The exterior retains a distinguished presence, complemented by an interior that has been carefully preserved to ensure a premium driving environment. Rigorously inspected to meet our professional standards for safety and longevity, this offering represents a sophisticated acquisition for the discerning motorist who prioritizes engineering excellence and enduring value.",
      "price": 33500.0,
